videos.headline: Storey connects with Pearson for 30-yard Hilltoppers TD
videos.description: With a pass up the middle, Western Kentucky's Ty Storey finds Jahcour Pearson to score the 30-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Storey connects with Pearson for 30-yard Hilltoppers TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hilltoppers' Jackson reels in long TD pass
videos.description: Western Kentucky's Ty Storey launches a 69-yard touchdown pass to Lucky Jackson giving the Hilltoppers a 14-7 lead over Charlotte.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hilltoppers' Jackson reels in long TD pass) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charlotte responds back with a 47-yard TD
videos.description: Chris Reynolds lets one fly up the middle 47 yards right into the hands of Charlotte's running back Benny LeMay to tie it up against Western Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Charlotte responds back with a 47-yard TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET
